---
title: Chicken Thigh Shawarma Pita Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Our chef-curated “perfect plates” are the answer to your dinner woes! Set out a sumptuous Mediterranean-style spread of tender, garlicky shawarma-spiced chicken thighs, fresh tomato-cucumber salad, zingy pickled onion, and warm pitas to wrap it all up, plus a creamy, tangy sauce for drizzling. Serve it all family style and order hummus and/or feta for even more choices!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a7d511ff70d218deffb341-3644f3bb.jpeg
